   "regime-CC?" store

\ Chord regime BB: R_decay < 0.5.
"R-decay-1000x" load 500 < "regime-BB?" store

\ Chord regime DD: R_decay > 1.5.
"R-decay-1000x" load 1500 > "regime-DD?" store

